### Project ignores
tmp/
.claude/settings.local.json
.claude/worktrees/
.idea/

### Python toolchain artifacts
__pycache__/
.pytest_cache/
.ruff_cache/
.coverage
.coverage.*

### UV local state
.venv/

### Beads / Dolt
# Per-clone bd state (Dolt working copy, lockfiles, runtime artifacts,
# per-machine metadata.json) is excluded by .beads/.gitignore (tracked
# itself). `.beads/config.yaml` IS tracked: it carries the server-mode
# connection block for the livespec-driver-claude Dolt tenant with NO
# per-machine project_id and NO password (the tenant password is
# supplied via the BEADS_DOLT_PASSWORD env var at bd-call time).
.beads-credential-key
*.env.local
